{
  "stem": "5328.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So I show it that a Jew is eating bacon.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That means I'm not Jewish.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I'm Christian if I eat bacon.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So that piece of bread and the bacon I kept in my hand.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I came to that farmer, to that Czechoslovakian farmer.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I asked him to help me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I introduced myself who I am.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So he-- he didn't answer nothing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He just took me by-- by-- by my arm.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He dragged me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I said-- and I thought he's dragged me to the Ukrainian or the SS man.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I said, please, and I start crying.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "If you cannot help me, don't harm me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Let me go.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And he drags me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "He drags me right in-- into his barn and open up the hay.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And there was my father hidden.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "So we met with my father together.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "We stayed with him for two weeks on that farm in the hay.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "At night, he let us in in the house.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And during the day, we were in the hay hidden in the barn.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Once, it was-- it was a Ukrainian or SS man came in and they start looking for Jews.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And they were with forks going in the hay.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "In just close to us, we were almost hit with the fork but didn't.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "So-- so he was afraid already to keep us, the Czechoslovakian farmer.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "He said, you have to go.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "I can keep you any longer.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Beside, we used to give-- we gave him some gold pieces for staying.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "But this-- he didn't care about it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "We gave him just like-- we thank you for it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "But he wouldn't let-- let us stay any longer.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "The was dangerous.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "It was dangerous for him, and it was dangerous for-- for his family and for us.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
